
INT ID(sum) LPAREN RPAREN
LBRACE
INT ID(i) COMMA ID(v) LBRACKET CT_INT(5) RBRACKET COMMA ID(s) SEMICOLON
ID(s) ASSIGN CT_INT(138) SEMICOLON
FOR LPAREN ID(i) ASSIGN CT_INT(0) SEMICOLON ID(i) LT CT_INT(5) SEMICOLON ID(i) ASSIGN ID(i) PLUS CT_INT(1) RPAREN LBRACE
ID(v) LBRACKET ID(i) RBRACKET ASSIGN ID(i) SEMICOLON
ID(s) ASSIGN ID(s) PLUS ID(v) LBRACKET ID(i) RBRACKET SEMICOLON
RBRACE
RETURN ID(s) SEMICOLON
RBRACE

VOID ID(main) LPAREN RPAREN
LBRACE
INT ID(i) COMMA ID(s) SEMICOLON
FOR LPAREN ID(i) ASSIGN CT_INT(0) SEMICOLON ID(i) LT CT_INT(1000000) SEMICOLON ID(i) ASSIGN ID(i) PLUS CT_INT(1) RPAREN
ID(s) ASSIGN ID(sum) LPAREN RPAREN SEMICOLON
ID(put_i) LPAREN ID(s) RPAREN SEMICOLON
RBRACE
